## Architecture

This project uses **feature-based architecture** with Riverpod for state management:

- **lib/{{projectName}}/app/** — App shell, routing (GoRouter)
- **lib/{{projectName}}/counter/** — Counter feature: provider + view
- **test/** — Mirror of lib/, unit + widget tests

Key conventions:

- Each feature owns its state (provider) and UI (view/) in one directory
- State is managed via Riverpod `StateNotifierProvider`
- All widgets use `const` constructors and `super.key`
- No `print()` — use a logging service for production
- Tests cover both provider logic (unit) and widget rendering (widget test)
